snippet.title: Hellbreach: Vegas - Wishlist Now on Steam
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1691320/Hellbreach_Vegas/

Demons are searching for a new home—what better place than Sin City? Play solo or in a team of up to four in this wave-based first-person shooter survival game. Fight to escape the hellbreach as the Viking demon army invades Las Vegas. How long can you survive?

Stay up to date with Hellbreach: Vegas and Iceberg Interactive:
